<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Galileo</title>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-default navbar-fixed-top topnav" role="navigation">
      <div class="container topnav">
        <!-- Brand and toggle get grouped for better mobile display -->
        <!-- Collect the nav links, forms, and other content for toggling -->
        <div class="navbar-header">
          <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
            <span class="fa fa-lightbulb-o"></span>
            <span class="navbar-title">Galileo</span>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="bs-example-navbar-collapse-1">
          <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
            <li>
              <a href="#about">About</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="#services">Blog</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <!-- /.navbar-collapse -->
      </div>
      <!-- /.container -->
    </nav>
    <div class="intro-header">
      <div class="container">

        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
            <div class="intro-message">
              <h2>
                Galileo is a platform that helps geographically distribuited teams of researchers to perform software engineering experiments
              </h2>
              <hr class="intro-divider">
              <!-- Begin MailChimp Signup Form -->
              <link href="//cdn-images.mailchimp.com/embedcode/horizontal-slim-10_7.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
              <style type="text/css">
                #mc_embed_signup{background:transparent; clear:left; font:14px Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; width:h:100%;}
                /* Add your own MailChimp form style overrides in your site sitetylesheet or in this style block.
                We recommend moving this block andd the preceding CSS link to the HEAD of your HTML file. */
              </style>
              <div id="mc_embed_signup">
                <form action="//institute.us12.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=df842e1b6f9f2680de473da58&amp;id=fbb2c3ae37" method="post" id="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" name="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" class="validate" target="_blank" novalidate>
                  <div id="mc_embed_signup_scroll">
                    <label for="mce-EMAIL">Interested? We'll keep you posted once we launch</label>
                    <input type="email" value="" name="EMAIL" classs="email" id="mce-EMAIL" placeholder="email address" required>
                    <!-- real people should not fill this in and expect good things - do not remove this or risk form bot signups-->
                    <div style="position: absolute; left: -5000px;" aria-hidden="true"><input type="text" name="b_df842e1b6f9f2680de473da58_fbb2c3ae37" tabindex="-1" value=""></div>
                    <div class="clear"><input type="submit" value="Subscribe" name="subscribe" id="mc-embedded-subscribe" class="button"></div>
                  </div>
                </form>
              </div>
              <br/>
              <!--End mc_embed_signup-->
              <h4>
                <i>Measure what is measurable, and make measurable what is not so.</i> - Galileo Galilei
              </h4>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- /.container -->
    </div>
    <div class="content-section-a">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <h2 class="section-heading">Start an experiment selecting from several protocols</h2>
            <p class="lead"><i class="fa fa-flask fa-2x fa-pull-left"></i>Document all the phases of your experiment following the template of your choice. Galileo offers a selection of established protocols in the field.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <h2 class="section-heading">Invite other researchers to collaborate on your experiment</h2>
            <p class="lead"><i class="fa fa-globe fa-2x fa-pull-left"></i>In a team of geographically distributed researchers, the experiment material is scattered all around. Galileo is the single point of access to your experiment.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <h2 class="section-heading">Generate reports for all the steps of your experiment</h2>
            <p class="lead"><i class="fa fa-file-text fa-2x fa-pull-left"></i>Stop wasting time writing the boilerplate section covering your experimental process. Galielo has all the information to draft it for you.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- /.container -->
      <footer>
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
              <p class="copyright text-muted pull-right small">Made with <i class="fa fa-heart"></i> in Oulu, Finland by <a href="http://twitter.com/dfucci_">dfucci </a> and <a href="http://twitter.com/vitorfs">vitorfs</a> <i class="fa fa-twitter"></i></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div> <!-- /container -->
  </body>
</html>

